{"ticketId":"56","id":"56-301","outcome":{"note":{}},"phase":"planning","at":804611260.050864,"detail":"---\n\n## Facts for the Planner — Issue #56: Make sure the README is up to date (and related docs)\n\n### 1. Project Identity & Live Surface\n\n| Fact | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| **Repo** | `iksnae\/vokda` (private) |\n| **Stack** | SvelteKit 4 (TypeScript) + AWS Amplify Gen2 + SAM Synthesis API |\n| **Package manager** | npm workspaces monorepo, Node >=20 |\n| **Live app** | https:\/\/vokda.iknsae.com |\n| **Live API** | https:\/\/api.vokda.iksnae.com |\n| **CI** | `.github\/workflows\/ci.yml` — `web-checks` job (typecheck, Svelte check, catalog freshness, build) on push to `main` and PRs |\n| **Test count** | 264 unit tests (vitest, per CLAUDE.md); ARCHITECTURE.md says 178 (stale) |\n| **Catalog scale** | 550 voices, 25 providers, 53 languages, 100% audio sample coverage |\n\n### 2. README.md — Current Gaps (vs CLAUDE.md truth)\n\nCLAUDE.md at the repo root is the comprehensive, up-to-date internal reference. README.md is a stale subset. Specific gaps:\n\n**§ Stack:**\n- Says *\"Catalog data: app-owned module (phase 1), API-backed later\"* — reality: static `voices.json` catalog at build time, SAM-deployed Synthesis API with 9 provider adapters, Amplify Gen2 backend (Cognito + AppSync + DynamoDB)\n- No mention of the Synthesis API, Amplify Gen2, or S3 audio storage\n\n**§ Repo Layout:**\n- Lists `packages\/shared` — the real package is `packages\/sdk` (`@vokda\/sdk` TypeScript SDK). `packages\/shared` is an empty placeholder directory\n- Missing: `sdks\/` (Go, Python, Rust), `scripts\/` (catalog generators), `specs\/` (feature plans), `extensions\/`\n\n**§ Quick Start:**\n- Only `npm install` + `npm run dev:web` + `.env` setup\n- Missing: Node >=20 requirement, `npm run dev:api`, `npm test`, `npm run check:web`, `npm run build:web`, `npm run build:sdk`\n\n**§ Product Docs:**\n- Lists 7 docs, but 14 `.md` files exist in `docs\/` plus 3 subdirectories\n- **Missing from list:** `VISION.md`, `DISCOVERY.md`, `SYNTHESIS_API.md`, `VOICE_CATALOG_EXPORT.md`, `GITHUB_SETUP.md`, `AMPLIFY_SETUP.md`, `voice-discovery-process.md`\n\n**§ CI\/CD:**\n- Brief but accurate. Could note specific checks (typecheck, Svelte check, catalog freshness, build).\n\n**§ Missing entirely:**\n- Live URLs (app + API)\n- Node version requirement\n- Test commands\n- SDK package mention\n- Any reference to synthesis, SSML editor, steering, or BYOK\n\n### 3. Related Docs — State\n\n| Doc | Status | Issue |\n|-----|--------|-------|\n| `CLAUDE.md` | **Current** | Comprehensive internal reference — source of truth for commands, file map, architecture, conventions |\n| `docs\/ARCHITECTURE.md` | **Current** | Up-to-date system overview, component map, data flow, infrastructure |\n| `docs\/ROADMAP.md` | **Current** | Reflects shipped + planned work accurately |\n| `docs\/SCHEMA.md` | **Current** | Full data model documentation including Steering |\n| `docs\/API.md` | **Current** | Index pointing to SYNTHESIS_API.md and DISCOVERY.md |\n| `docs\/SYNTHESIS_API.md` | **Current** | Full API reference |\n| `docs\/DISCOVERY.md` | **Current** | Voice discovery user guide |\n| `docs\/VISION.md` | **Current** | Product vision |\n| `docs\/VOICE_CATALOG_EXPORT.md` | **Current** | Export format spec |\n| `docs\/PROVIDER_IDS.md` | **Current** | References a `CHANGELOG.md` that **does not exist** |\n| `docs\/GLOSSARY.md` | **Current** | Terminology reference |\n| `docs\/AMPLIFY_BACKEND_GEN2.md` | **Current** | Amplify Gen2 setup |\n| `docs\/AMPLIFY_SETUP.md` | **Current** | Amplify hosting checklist |\n| `docs\/GITHUB_SETUP.md` | **Current** | GitHub setup checklist |\n| **`docs\/voice-discovery-process.md`** | **STALE** | Says 130 voices across 8 providers; reality is 550 across 25. References old scripts and workflows that may no longer match |\n| `docs\/specs\/hub-architecture.md` | Current | Phase 3 hub spec |\n| `specs\/VISION.md` | Current | Duplicate of `docs\/VISION.md` (identical content) |\n\n### 4. Key Decisions Recorded\n\n- README.md is the public entry point — update it to reflect actual stack, commands, repo layout, complete product docs list, and live URLs, drawing from CLAUDE.md as the internal truth\n- `docs\/voice-discovery-process.md` is stale (130→550 voices, 8→25 providers) and needs updating or removal\n- No `CHANGELOG.md` exists despite `PROVIDER_IDS.md` referencing it — out of scope for this issue but noted\n- `specs\/VISION.md` is a duplicate of `docs\/VISION.md` — should not exist in two places; one should be canonical\n\n### 5. What does NOT need updating\n\n- `CLAUDE.md` — already comprehensive and current\n- `docs\/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `ROADMAP.md`, `SCHEMA.md`, `API.md`, `SYNTHESIS_API.md`, `DISCOVERY.md`, `VISION.md`, `GLOSSARY.md`, `PROVIDER_IDS.md`, `AMPLIFY_BACKEND_GEN2.md`, `AMPLIFY_SETUP.md`, `GITHUB_SETUP.md` — all current\n- `PRD.md` and `IDEA.md` — foundational specs, intentionally static\n- `package.json` — current and correct"}
